算了，不要吵了
Let's not quarrel

204
00:12:35,321 --> 00:12:36,015
什么算呀？
Leave it?

205
00:12:36,122 --> 00:12:37,612
他撞了人还那么凶
He is in the wrong, yet is so fierce

206
00:12:37,990 --> 00:12:39,252
兰丝，那怕那个三寸钉
Don't be scared of this shorty

207
00:12:39,358 --> 00:12:40,382
什么三寸钉？
Who are you calling shorty?

208
00:12:40,893 --> 00:12:42,121
你说我？
Are you yelling at me?

209
00:12:43,763 --> 00:12:44,491
说声对不起
Just say sorry

210
00:12:44,597 --> 00:12:45,086
什么？
What?

211
00:12:45,197 --> 00:12:46,255
是你不对嘛
You are in the wrong

212
00:12:46,365 --> 00:12:47,423
我不对？
Me? Wrong?

213
00:12:48,434 --> 00:12:49,332
说啊
Say it

214
00:12:49,435 --> 00:12:50,163
你真的要我说？
You really want me to?

215
00:12:50,269 --> 00:12:50,928
说呀
Say it

216
00:12:52,638 --> 00:12:53,332
要说就你说
You say it

217
00:12:53,439 --> 00:12:54,906
我积奇从来不认输的
l, Jackie never apologize

218
00:12:55,641 --> 00:12:57,006
你不说就别想出去
lf you don't, you are not leaving

219
00:12:59,278 --> 00:13:00,905
不出去就不出去，会死啊
So l will stay, l fear not

220
00:13:01,013 --> 00:13:02,207
大不了再回英国
The worse is l will return to England

221
00:13:08,687 --> 00:13:09,847
对不起
Sorry

222
00:13:09,955 --> 00:13:11,752
我这位朋友小孩子脾气
He is like a kid

223
00:13:12,892 --> 00:13:14,359
我代他向这位小姐道歉
l apologize on his behalf

224
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:15,857
小姐，真是不好意思
Miss, l am sorry

225
00:13:23,736 --> 00:13:24,998
干爹，媚姨
Godpa, Aunt May

226
00:13:25,104 --> 00:13:25,866
老爷
Master

227
00:13:26,605 --> 00:13:27,299
坐
Have a seat

228
00:13:34,146 --> 00:13:35,078
庄臣
Johnson

229
00:13:35,181 --> 00:13:37,911
我叫你回来是想告诉你
The reason l have asked you
to come back...

230
00:13:38,184 --> 00:13:39,242
我决定退休了
is to inform you that l am retiring

231
00:13:39,485 --> 00:13:40,509
您要退休？
You are retiring?

232
00:13:40,619 --> 00:13:44,680
麻雀馆和俱乐部全交给你媚姨管理
Aunt May will manage
the mahjong house and club

233
00:13:45,257 --> 00:13:46,849
你不要回去念书了
Don't pursue your studies in England

234
00:13:47,827 --> 00:13:50,057
留在这儿帮媚姨的忙，管管帐
Stay and help your Aunt May,
keep the books

235
00:13:53,098 --> 00:13:54,827
麻雀馆不是普通生意
The mahjong business
is a specialised field

236
00:13:54,934 --> 00:13:56,765
不熟悉这行根本没法去做
lt's difficult if you are not an expert

237
00:13:57,036 --> 00:13:59,266
庄臣连一幅牌有多少章都不知道
Johnson does not know anything
about mahjong

238
00:13:59,371 --> 00:14:01,202
叫他来帮忙，那不是...
To ask him to help, that...

239
00:14:02,908 --> 00:14:04,273
我叫他管那儿的帐
l have asked him to watch the accounts

240
00:14:04,376 --> 00:14:05,536
又不是叫他坐馆
Not oversee the operation

241
00:14:06,178 --> 00:14:07,509
他是学电脑的
He specializes in computers

242
00:14:07,613 --> 00:14:09,240
对那些数目字一定很敏感
And should be good with figures

243
00:14:09,448 --> 00:14:10,380
说得那么容易
Easier said than done

244
00:14:10,482 --> 00:14:11,414
我跟了你十年
l've followed you for 10 years

245
00:14:11,517 --> 00:14:12,609
你还是不相信我？
You still do not trust me?

246
00:14:17,289 --> 00:14:19,655
庄臣，以后你就管帐
Johnson, from now the accounts are yours

247
00:14:19,758 --> 00:14:20,986
其他的事由媚姨作主
Aunt May will decide on other matters

248
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:21,885
是，干爹
Yes

249
00:14:22,962 --> 00:14:23,587
根叔
Uncle Jin

250
00:14:24,163 --> 00:14:25,494
这位是...
This is...

251
00:14:25,598 --> 00:14:27,031
老爷的干儿子
the step son of master

252
00:14:27,132 --> 00:14:27,826
他叫阿辉
His name is Ah Fai

253
00:14:28,434 --> 00:14:30,493
是你媚姨的得力助手
And is your Aunt May's side kick

254
00:14:30,603 --> 00:14:31,695
哦，庄少爷
Oh, master Yau

255
00:14:32,104 --> 00:14:33,093
今天很旺
This is a good business day

256
00:14:33,372 --> 00:14:34,498
一直都是这样
lt's been like this

257
00:14:35,207 --> 00:14:36,174
如果不是这样
lf not for this...

258
00:14:36,275 --> 00:14:38,641
你媚姨也不会要死要活的霸着
Your Aunt May would not have
struggled to grab it

259
00:14:46,151 --> 00:14:46,981
别生气嘛
Don't be angry

260
00:14:47,753 --> 00:14:49,277
你干爹有九间麻雀馆
Your Godpa has 9 mahjong houses

261
00:14:49,388 --> 00:14:50,286
三间俱乐部
3 club houses

262
00:14:50,656 --> 00:14:51,782
你看看
Take a look

263
00:14:52,291 --> 00:14:56,284
日夜都这么热闹，生意好起来
lt's busy like this day and night

264
00:14:56,562 --> 00:14:58,587
每个月都有两百多万的进帐
When it's good we get 2 million
each month

265
00:15:12,077 --> 00:15:12,805
碰
Pung

266
00:15:15,948 --> 00:15:16,676
看着他
Keep an eye on him

267
00:15:20,519 --> 00:15:23,352
马不停蹄，马上就来看着了
You have come to check
without delay, huh !

268
00:15:24,857 --> 00:15:25,915
根叔带我来看看
Uncle Jin is showing me around

269
00:15:26,292 --> 00:15:28,419
说不定以后你就是老板了
You might be the future boss

270
00:15:28,961 --> 00:15:31,623
到时候我牌瘾来了想玩几铺
When l have the urge to play
a couple of hands

271
00:15:31,730 --> 00:15:33,595
不知道可不可以呢，根叔
...would you allow me, Uncle Jin

272
00:15:33,699 --> 00:15:34,597
不敢当，媚姨
You are too kind, Aunt May

273
00:15:35,734 --> 00:15:37,634
在英国好吃好住
You have an easy life in England

274
00:15:37,736 --> 00:15:39,567
何必回来跟我争这口辛苦饭
Why return and vie for this difficultjob

275
00:15:40,773 --> 00:15:41,831
谁跟你争呀？
Who is vying with you?

276
00:15:42,107 --> 00:15:43,369
我是尊重干爹的意思
l respect Godpa's wish

277
00:15:44,009 --> 00:15:44,941
我们这行饭
ln our line of business

278
00:15:45,044 --> 00:15:46,375
你以为那么容易吃的吗？
Do you think it is easy?

279
00:16:26,085 --> 00:16:28,952
光是这两下子就够你学了
Only this would take you
some time to learn

280
00:16:29,321 --> 00:16:30,788
用点心吧
Apply yourself

281
00:16:30,889 --> 00:16:33,414
要不然有人会很失望的
Or else someone
would be very disappointed

282
00:16:40,432 --> 00:16:43,060
有人出老千...
Someone is cheating

283
00:17:09,561 --> 00:17:10,585
丘太太，你找我？
Mrs. Yau, you've been looking for me?

284
00:17:11,096 --> 00:17:12,085
今天晚上有几个大客
There are some big clients tonight

285
00:17:12,197 --> 00:17:13,425
你到上面准备一下
Make the necessary preparations

286
00:17:14,066 --> 00:17:15,397
玩真的还是玩假的？
Are you playing for real?

287
00:17:15,501 --> 00:17:17,128
真也好，假也好
Regardless

288
00:17:17,236 --> 00:17:18,464
总之我要赢
l want to win

289
00:17:18,904 --> 00:17:19,734
好，我会办妥的
OK. l will make
the necessary preparations

290
00:17:23,375 --> 00:17:25,502
庄臣，你留十万块钱给我
Johnson, leave me $100,000

291
00:17:25,744 --> 00:17:27,609
干什么？我已经结好帐了
For what? l have closed the book

292
00:17:28,647 --> 00:17:30,581
不是要等你干爹开口你才肯给吧？
Would it take Godpa to instruct you?

293
00:17:31,817 --> 00:17:33,045
庄少爷
Master Yau

294
00:17:33,152 --> 00:17:35,313
你就照媚姨的意思去做吧
Do as your Aunt May says

295
00:17:36,522 --> 00:17:38,649
拿着鸡毛当令箭
Playing the boss

296
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:44,155
今晚这两个家伙有灾受了
These two guys are in trouble tonight

297
00:17:49,268 --> 00:17:50,166
九筒
9 circles

298
00:17:56,809 --> 00:17:59,141
你媚姨现在向阿辉要九条
Aunt May is asking Ah Fai for 9 bamboos

299
00:18:01,413 --> 00:18:02,107
九条
9 bamboos

300
00:18:02,347 --> 00:18:03,211
碰
Pung

301
00:18:05,884 --> 00:18:06,782
又要发财了
She wants Green Dragon again

302
00:18:09,054 --> 00:18:09,782
五筒
5 circles

303
00:18:12,057 --> 00:18:12,853
这一章
This tile...

304
00:18:12,958 --> 00:18:13,515
打啦
Go ahead

305
00:18:13,959 --> 00:18:15,119
怎么打得出去呢
How can you play like this?

306
00:18:15,360 --> 00:18:16,292
又动手脚了
There you go again

307
00:18:17,262 --> 00:18:18,229
算了吧，弃权了
Forget it, give it up

308
00:18:21,300 --> 00:18:22,790
混一色对对胡自摸发财
Full Flush, All sets

309
00:18:22,901 --> 00:18:24,061
刚刚好八番
Eight points

310
00:18:24,536 --> 00:18:26,470
发财你也摸得着
You are lucky to draw the Green Dragon

311
00:18:26,572 --> 00:18:27,504
这怎么打得过你呀
How can we beat you

312
00:18:28,340 --> 00:18:30,365
真是，听四章牌都胡不过你
l lost even though
l get the good combination

313
00:18:30,642 --> 00:18:31,438
还怎么打呀
How can we beat you

314
00:18:34,113 --> 00:18:34,875
碰
Pung

315
00:18:42,020 --> 00:18:44,648
这一铺媚姨拆牌给阿辉吃
Your Aunt May is favouring Ah Fai's game

316
00:18:46,625 --> 00:18:47,114
东
East

317
00:18:47,226 --> 00:18:48,022
碰
Pung

318
00:18:49,027 --> 00:18:49,322
两番
Two points

319
00:18:49,428 --> 00:18:50,520
怎么搞的？
What has happened?

320
00:18:50,896 --> 00:18:52,056
你看我这幅牌多漂亮？
Look how beautifully l am set up !

321
00:18:52,164 --> 00:18:52,789
我也漂亮啊
Me too

322
00:18:52,898 --> 00:18:53,660
你怎么这么打牌？
Why do you play like this?

323
00:18:54,533 --> 00:18:55,192
你什么牌？
What do you have?

324
00:18:55,534 --> 00:18:56,228
我看看
Let me see

325
00:18:56,835 --> 00:18:57,824
你看我的牌干什么？
Why do you look at mine?

326
00:18:57,936 --> 00:18:58,960
你管我打什么牌？
What do you care how l play?

327
00:18:59,471 --> 00:19:00,631
你教我打啊
You show me

328
00:19:00,739 --> 00:19:02,229
难道我打八筒啊？
Did you want me to discard 8 Circles?

329
00:19:02,508 --> 00:19:03,497
打下一铺吧
Play the next game

330
00:19:07,579 --> 00:19:09,240
别乱打，九章了
Don't mess around

331
00:19:10,516 --> 00:19:11,505
干吗那是假的
He is faking it

332
00:19:12,417 --> 00:19:12,849
二万
Twenty thousand

333
00:19:12,951 --> 00:19:13,713
碰
Pung

334
00:19:14,186 --> 00:19:15,653
这回轮到你包十二章了
This time you will lose

335
00:19:17,089 --> 00:19:17,885
六万
Sixty thousand

336
00:19:22,661 --> 00:19:23,389
四条
4 bamboos

337
00:19:38,377 --> 00:19:39,275
摸来了
l get it

338
00:19:41,513 --> 00:19:43,140
我以为要包自摸
l thought l had to cover all winnings

339
00:19:43,248 --> 00:19:44,840
原来还有钱收啊
But it looks l have money to collect

340
00:19:45,651 --> 00:19:47,175
四圈都不开胡
You didn't win in four rounds

341
00:19:47,286 --> 00:19:48,981
一开胡就来个诈胡
Foul in the opening round

342
00:20:00,365 --> 00:20:02,094
这间弹子房是郭柱开的
This joint was started by Mr. Kwok Chu

343
00:20:02,668 --> 00:20:03,828
你媚姨时常上来
Your Aunt May comes frequently

344
00:20:05,037 --> 00:20:06,937
根叔，她是不是上来打弹子
Uncle Jin, she has not come for the games

345
00:20:07,739 --> 00:20:09,206
她醉翁之意不在酒
Her interest is not in the games

346
00:20:09,308 --> 00:20:10,070
明白吗？
Do you get it?

347
00:20:44,443 --> 00:20:45,205
真厉害
You are good

348
00:21:10,168 --> 00:21:10,793
谁？
Who is it?

349
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:19,802
救命呀...
Help ...

350
00:21:19,911 --> 00:21:20,639
郭先生
Mr. Kwok

351
00:21:21,013 --> 00:21:22,002
你是谁？
Who are you?

352
00:21:22,114 --> 00:21:23,240
他是我们少爷的朋友
He is our young master's friend

353
00:21:23,715 --> 00:21:24,647
我是问你？
l am asking you

354
00:21:24,750 --> 00:21:26,775
我叫JackyChan
l am Jacky Chan

355
00:21:29,755 --> 00:21:30,847
媚姨
Aunt May

356
00:21:35,060 --> 00:21:35,856
庄少爷
Master Yau

357
00:21:36,595 --> 00:21:38,028
你怎么会到这儿来玩？
Why have you come here?

358
00:21:38,897 --> 00:21:39,488
我不来
lf l didn't come

359
00:21:39,598 --> 00:21:40,997
怎么看得见这么好的戏？
Would l have seen such a good show?

360
00:21:41,099 --> 00:21:41,724
少爷
Young Master

361
00:21:42,267 --> 00:21:43,359
难道你不知道你干妈
Don't you know your Godma

362
00:21:43,468 --> 00:21:45,129
要开一间弹子房吗？
Wants to run a pool joint as well?

363
00:21:45,237 --> 00:21:47,637
原来干妈想开...
So Godma wants to open ...

364
00:21:48,573 --> 00:21:50,268
我是说开弹子房
l am saying open a pool joint

365
00:21:50,776 --> 00:21:52,801
怪不得老来找郭先生
No wonder she frequently sees Mr. Kwok

366
00:21:53,345 --> 00:21:54,903
你年纪轻轻
Young as you are

367
00:21:55,213 --> 00:21:56,646
得点颜色就想开染房
You are over ambitious

368
00:21:56,848 --> 00:21:57,177
既然你知道
Since you know

369
00:21:57,282 --> 00:21:58,715
就不应该这样对我干爹
You shouldn't treat my Godpa like this

370
00:22:01,687 --> 00:22:03,211
管理麻雀馆
To run a mahjong house

371
00:22:03,322 --> 00:22:07,452
牌术要精，眼要灵，反应要快
You need to be good at the game
& have quick reflexes

372
00:22:08,293 --> 00:22:10,227
还要对付那些千王千霸
And deal with those con men

373
00:22:11,296 --> 00:22:13,287
不是你想像中那么容易
lt is more difficult than you think

374
00:22:13,932 --> 00:22:15,092
我知道不容易
l know it isn't easy

375
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:16,497
不过我想试一试
But l want to try

376
00:22:16,601 --> 00:22:18,831
是啊，我们少爷那么聪明
Yes, our master is smart

377
00:22:18,937 --> 00:22:20,234
我相信他很快就学会
l am sure he will learn quickly

378
00:22:20,339 --> 00:22:20,998
根叔
Uncle Jin

379
00:22:21,106 --> 00:22:23,574
你也算是打了几十年牌
You have played mahjong for many years

380
00:22:23,675 --> 00:22:25,575
还是拿不到雀爷名衔
But have not been crowned
King of Mahjong

381
00:22:27,479 --> 00:22:28,673
你真的有兴趣？
Are you really interested?

382
00:22:28,780 --> 00:22:30,338
本来没有，现在有
Not before, but l am now

383
00:22:30,716 --> 00:22:31,648
为什么？
Why?

384
00:22:31,750 --> 00:22:34,116
我觉得麻将是一种高尚的娱乐
Mahjong is a high class entertainment

385
00:22:34,219 --> 00:22:35,914
可以训练精密的头脑
lt can drill the brain

386
00:22:36,021 --> 00:22:37,079
灵活的思考
To be agile

387
00:22:37,189 --> 00:22:38,451
又可以敦众睦邻
Widen your network and make friends

388
00:22:38,690 --> 00:22:39,816
培养合作精神
Develop team spirit

389
00:22:40,225 --> 00:22:43,456
那就是说你干爹开麻将馆让人赌钱
Are you saying
your Godpa's mahjong business

390
00:22:43,562 --> 00:22:44,586
是不对了？
... is wrong?

391
00:22:44,696 --> 00:22:45,560
不是
Not at all

392
00:22:45,664 --> 00:22:47,598
只要光明磊落，大公无私
So long as it is transparent and fair

393
00:22:47,699 --> 00:22:48,666
都是正行生意
lt is a legitimate business

394
00:22:49,201 --> 00:22:52,170
只怕有些人借题发挥，伤天害理
Except for those who do immoral things

395
00:22:52,270 --> 00:22:55,501
哦，这是你来抽我的后腿
So you are setting me up

396
00:22:55,607 --> 00:22:56,835
告我的状
Telling on me

397
00:22:58,710 --> 00:22:59,938
我做错什么？
What have l done wrong?

398
00:23:00,045 --> 00:23:01,273
说出来怕你丢脸
lt would be bad for you if l told

399
00:23:04,282 --> 00:23:05,214
庄少爷
Master Chong

400
00:23:05,317 --> 00:23:07,751
我看你是吃不到葡萄说葡萄酸
The way l see it, it's just sour grapes

401
00:23:08,653 --> 00:23:10,416
借题发挥的是你不是我
You are the one trying to cause trouble

402
00:23:12,023 --> 00:23:13,183
不要在这儿针锋相对了
Stop your confrontation now

403
00:23:14,626 --> 00:23:16,491
庄臣，你既然有意思
Johnson, since you are interested

404
00:23:16,595 --> 00:23:18,222
我给你六个月的时间学习
l will give you 6 months to learn

405
00:23:19,297 --> 00:23:22,266
在十月二十七号正午
At noon on 27th October

406
00:23:22,367 --> 00:23:24,335
你和媚姨在麻将台上
You and Aunt May will decide by mahjong

407
00:23:24,436 --> 00:23:26,563
