00:29:42,580 --> 00:29:46,573
打麻将分四个阶段
There are 4 stages in mahjong playing

529
00:29:46,684 --> 00:29:51,053
顾自家，盯下家
protect yourself, exterminate your

530
00:29:51,156 --> 00:29:54,614
骗上家，砍对家
Delude, attack the opposition

531
00:29:54,726 --> 00:29:56,523
师傅，你别教那么多
Teacher, don't teach so much

532
00:29:56,628 --> 00:29:57,925
我连自己都顾不了
l can't even protect myself

533
00:29:58,196 --> 00:30:01,427
你慢慢来嘛，这个不能够心急
Be patient, you can't rush it

534
00:30:01,533 --> 00:30:06,630
麻将这玩意变化多端，趣味无穷
Mahjong is a rich game
with endless possibilities

535
00:30:06,738 --> 00:30:08,137
打得不好的呢
Those less skilled

536
