要靠七分运气，三分技术
require 70% luck and 30% technique

537
00:30:12,010 --> 00:30:13,102
打得好的呢
For the skilled

538
00:30:13,211 --> 00:30:15,771
七分技术，三分运气
They need only 30% luck

539
00:30:15,880 --> 00:30:18,371
不过，没有逢赌必赢的
But no one can always win

540
00:30:19,484 --> 00:30:22,112
你要记住，下场三件事
There are 3 important factors to a game

541
00:30:22,353 --> 00:30:25,186
天时，地利，人和
Opportunity, timing and human factor

542
00:30:33,832 --> 00:30:35,322
什么事？什么事？
What's happening?

543
