Why?

608
00:34:24,729 --> 00:34:26,924
第一，你进了屋里还戴着帽
Firstly you wear a hat indoors

609
00:34:28,699 --> 00:34:31,099
第二，这里只有你一个人抽烟斗
Secondly you are the only one with a pipe

610
00:34:31,736 --> 00:34:33,863
第三，现在又不下雨
Thirdly it is not raining

611
00:34:33,971 --> 00:34:35,165
你穿什么风雨衣
But you're wearing a rain coat

612
00:34:35,273 --> 00:34:35,830
不用脱
Keep it on

613
00:34:35,940 --> 00:34:36,531
为什么？
Why?

614
00:34:36,641 --> 00:34:37,505
他的意思是说
He means

615
00:34:37,608 --> 00:34:39,337
当你是露体狂，就更加难看
lt's worse if you're taken for a flasher

616
00:34:39,444 --> 00:34:40,433
对对对
Right...

617
00:34:45,316 --> 00:34:46,408
一六四七，一六四九
1647, 1649

618
00:34:46,517 --> 00:34:48,212
有人到，各就各位
Someone's arriving, take your places

619
00:34:52,090 --> 00:34:54,081
探长，不像啊
Detective, this doesn't look like it

620
00:34:54,192 --> 00:34:55,989
线人说是两个老头
The informant said two old guys

621
00:34:56,094 --> 00:34:57,857
带着白粉来给刀疤佬的
Will come and give cocaine to Scar Face

622
00:34:59,030 --> 00:34:59,758
你知不知道
Do you know why

623
00:34:59,864 --> 00:35:01,422
为什么你做了二十年探员
You have been a detective for 20 years

624
00:35:01,532 --> 00:35:02,863
还没有升级呀？
And yet haven't been promoted?

625
00:35:02,967 --> 00:35:04,093
知道
Yes

626
00:35:04,202 --> 00:35:05,965
因为每次我们跟强盗开火的时候
Each time we open fire on thugs

627
00:35:06,070 --> 00:35:07,970
一定打伤两三个队员
We wound our own guys

628
00:35:08,072 --> 00:35:10,540
还有啊，你lQ零蛋
Also your lQ is zero

629
00:35:11,142 --> 00:35:12,769
不错，探长说得对
Detective is right

630
00:35:12,877 --> 00:35:13,571
快去抓人吧
Go catch your man

631
00:35:13,811 --> 00:35:16,371
等一下，你们现在想怎么办？
Wait, what do you want to do?

632
00:35:18,349 --> 00:35:18,906
知不知道
Do you know why...

633
00:35:19,016 --> 00:35:20,677
为什么我做了三十年的探长
Having been a detective for over 30 years

634
00:35:20,785 --> 00:35:22,377
还升不上去做警务处长？
l am still not a Chief?

635
00:35:22,487 --> 00:35:23,647
不知道
l don't know

636
00:35:23,754 --> 00:35:25,585
因为我没有开除你们
That's because l haven't fired you guys

637
00:35:26,991 --> 00:35:27,753
兄弟
Brother

638
00:35:29,560 --> 00:35:30,686
什么兄弟？
What Brother?

639
00:35:31,062 --> 00:35:32,324
反正是兄弟了
Just Brother

640
00:35:32,430 --> 00:35:33,692
你知不知道我姓什么？
You know my surname?

641
00:35:34,565 --> 00:35:35,930
总之姓什么也是兄弟
Regardless we're brothers

642
00:35:36,033 --> 00:35:38,365
我姓元颜耶律督，九代单传
l am the devil-incarnate

643
00:35:38,469 --> 00:35:39,333
什么兄弟？
What brother?

644
00:35:40,705 --> 00:35:41,194
行
OK

645
00:35:42,306 --> 00:35:43,466
四海之内皆兄弟
All men are brothers

646
00:35:43,574 --> 00:35:45,906
姓什么也是一样，是不是？
Regardless of their names, right?

647
00:35:46,010 --> 00:35:47,204
伙计，普洱
Waiter, Pu er tea

648
00:35:47,311 --> 00:35:48,141
来了
Coming

649
00:35:58,823 --> 00:36:00,757
你们两个是不是来捣乱的？
Are you two messing around?

650
00:36:00,992 --> 00:36:02,482
不是，我们是来找人的
No, we're looking for someone

651
00:36:02,593 --> 00:36:03,855
找人？找谁？
Who?

652
00:36:05,630 --> 00:36:06,824
刀疤佬
Scar Face

653
00:36:07,832 --> 00:36:10,096
刀疤佬？
Scar Face?

654
00:36:10,902 --> 00:36:12,392
对，到底哪个才是呀？
Yes, where is he?

655
00:36:13,504 --> 00:36:15,199
你们不会大声叫吗？
Why don't you call him?

656
00:36:17,074 --> 00:36:20,840
刀疤佬
Scar Face

657
00:36:25,516 --> 00:36:26,448
坏了
This looks bad

658
00:36:26,551 --> 00:36:27,950
大疤，中疤，小疤
Big, medium and small scar faces

659
00:36:28,052 --> 00:36:29,815
全来了，到底哪个才是呀？
Which one is Scar Face?

660
00:36:29,921 --> 00:36:30,819
我是
l am

661
00:36:39,964 --> 00:36:41,625
你就是刀疤佬呀？
You are Scar Face?

662
00:36:41,732 --> 00:36:42,960
我叫刀疤成
l'm Scar Face

663
00:36:43,367 --> 00:36:44,766
成哥，我们是自己弟兄
Brother Shing, we're brothers

664
00:36:44,869 --> 00:36:46,393
有事想请你帮忙
We need your help

665
00:36:47,171 --> 00:36:47,967
成哥
Brother Shing

666
00:36:48,072 --> 00:36:50,973
这两个笨蛋是土包子
These two are bumpkins

667
00:36:51,075 --> 00:36:53,737
不是，不是，我们不是土包子
No, no, we are not

668
00:36:53,978 --> 00:36:54,876
有何为证？
What's your proof?

669
00:36:55,146 --> 00:36:56,579
有诗为证
Poetry recitation

670
00:36:56,681 --> 00:36:58,205
诗怎么说？
What does it say?

671
00:36:58,316 --> 00:36:59,408
这...
Well...

672
00:37:01,552 --> 00:37:03,383
头发生疮糯米池
Boils grow from my hair

673
00:37:03,487 --> 00:37:06,923
家贫...
Family is poor...

674
00:37:08,893 --> 00:37:10,190
家贫赌极都要输
But l keep losing when l gamble

675
00:37:12,129 --> 00:37:16,327
万望...
l pray...

676
00:37:19,203 --> 00:37:20,500
万望阿叔点醒我
You will guide me

677
00:37:20,972 --> 00:37:22,234
犹记花亭结义时
Remember our pledge

678
00:37:22,940 --> 00:37:24,498
犹记蜜桃成熟时
When the fruit is ripe

679
00:37:29,313 --> 00:37:30,780
你们两个来捣乱的？
Are you two messing around?

680
00:37:30,881 --> 00:37:32,178
不是，成哥
No, Brother Shing

681
00:37:32,283 --> 00:37:34,444
他平时懒，这诗没念熟
He is lazy and hasn't memorized it well

682
00:37:46,864 --> 00:37:48,593
你们两个来找我干什么？
What do you two want with me?

683
00:37:48,699 --> 00:37:49,256
是不是想做
Do you want to become...

684
00:37:49,367 --> 00:37:52,359
今年第一百六十八凶杀案的主角？
The 168th murder of the year ?

685
00:37:52,637 --> 00:37:55,003
不是，我们是来找燕西楼的
No, we are here for Yin Xi Liu

686
00:37:57,275 --> 00:37:58,537
燕西楼？
Yin Xi Liu?

687
00:37:58,643 --> 00:37:59,405
是啊
Yes

688
00:38:00,011 --> 00:38:02,536
好了，他跟燕西楼一定是好朋友
Good, he must be friends with Yin

689
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:03,608
朋友
Good buddies

690
00:38:04,282 --> 00:38:05,874
你知不知道我为什么叫刀疤成？
Do you know why l am called Scar Face?

691
00:38:06,884 --> 00:38:07,908
我早就想问你
l had wanted to ask you

692
00:38:08,019 --> 00:38:10,579
你的脸又白又滑嫩
Your face is fair and smooth

693
00:38:10,688 --> 00:38:11,985
连一颗暗疮都没有
There is not even a pimple

694
00:38:12,256 --> 00:38:13,553
坏在我这儿有
Too bad l have a scar here

695
00:38:14,592 --> 00:38:17,493
这是燕西楼把我害成这样的
Caused by Yin

696
00:38:18,396 --> 00:38:19,829
我发过誓
l swore

697
00:38:19,930 --> 00:38:22,125
要把燕西楼的名字改成刀疤楼
l will scar Yin in revenge

698
00:38:23,367 --> 00:38:24,459
就算做不到
Even if l don't

699
00:38:24,568 --> 00:38:25,728
也要找他的亲戚朋友
l'll find his friends and relatives

700
00:38:25,836 --> 00:38:27,064
姨妈姑姑来补数
To pay for his debt

701
00:38:28,139 --> 00:38:30,505
我们不是他亲戚...
We are not his relatives...

702
00:38:32,877 --> 00:38:34,139
你们准备改名字吧
Prepare to change your names

703
00:38:39,950 --> 00:38:41,281
这可不是闹着玩的
This is no joke

704
00:38:41,519 --> 00:38:43,214
快点走吧...
Let's get out of here...

705
00:38:46,023 --> 00:38:47,786
他们在这儿，快点追
They are here, get them quick

706
00:39:02,206 --> 00:39:04,800
线人说送白粉的怎会变成打架？
Did the informant expect this
to turn into a fight?

707
00:39:05,209 --> 00:39:06,972
不要相信线人说的
Don't trust the informant totally

708
00:39:07,078 --> 00:39:08,773
打架也是犯法，抓人
Fighting is also illegal, make arrests

709
00:39:21,559 --> 00:39:22,253
不许动
Don't move

710
00:39:30,234 --> 00:39:31,132
枪啊
Gun

711
00:39:32,903 --> 00:39:34,632
积奇...
Jackie...

712
00:39:36,140 --> 00:39:37,232
积奇，走啊
Jackie, flee

713
00:39:42,613 --> 00:39:44,012
线人没说有人私藏军火
Nobody said anything about arms dealing

714
00:39:44,448 --> 00:39:45,506
怎么会有人开枪？
Why did they open fire ?

715
00:39:46,217 --> 00:39:48,048
好在还剩一颗子弹
Luckily there's a bullet left

716
00:39:48,152 --> 00:39:49,278
探长，探长
Detective, detective

717
00:39:49,387 --> 00:39:51,082
看开一点，何必自杀
Cheer up, why commit suicide

718
00:39:51,889 --> 00:39:56,019
你告诉我，是谁给你这个消息的？
Tell me who gave you this information

719
00:40:21,585 --> 00:40:22,574
吵醒你了
l woke you

720
00:40:23,788 --> 00:40:24,880
我想见见你
l wanted to see you

721
00:40:32,096 --> 00:40:34,394
你有心要做的事一定会成功的
Put your heart into it
and you will succeed

722
00:40:34,665 --> 00:40:37,293
不要遇到挫折就灰心
Don't give up when faced with hurdles

723
00:40:38,702 --> 00:40:40,670
我不是灰心，是死心
l feel totally hopeless

724
00:40:41,605 --> 00:40:43,163
你叫我到哪儿去找燕西楼？
Where can l find Yin ?!

725
00:40:45,342 --> 00:40:47,276
我明天飞去法国，星期三回来
l'm off to France tomorrow,
will return Wednesday

726
00:40:47,378 --> 00:40:48,367
你来接我飞机
Come and pick me up

727
00:40:55,953 --> 00:40:56,885
来了很久？
Been waiting long?

728
00:40:56,987 --> 00:40:58,614
是啊，一个钟头了
Yes, for an hour

729
00:40:58,722 --> 00:40:59,654
怎么那么迟？
What's the delay?

730
00:40:59,757 --> 00:41:01,247
我临时调班，转了飞机
l switched flights

731
00:41:02,326 --> 00:41:03,452
你的小朋友呢？
Where's your friend?

732
00:41:03,561 --> 00:41:04,357
在那边
Over there

733
00:41:05,896 --> 00:41:09,696
庄臣，庄臣，过来呀
Johnson, come here

734
00:41:17,441 --> 00:41:20,205
我给你介绍，他是我大哥燕西楼
My brother Yin Xi Liu

735
00:41:32,423 --> 00:41:34,584
平师傅有没有告诉你
Has Ping told you

736
00:41:34,692 --> 00:41:36,319
我收徒弟是三不教
l don't teach 3 kinds of people

737
00:41:36,427 --> 00:41:37,121
三不教？
3 kinds?

738
00:41:37,595 --> 00:41:38,619
有没有硬币？
Got a coin ?

739
00:41:41,065 --> 00:41:41,656
有啊
Yes

740
00:41:44,935 --> 00:41:46,869
你伸出两只手指照我的意思做
Show me 2 fingers and listen

741
00:41:48,038 --> 00:41:50,131
干什么？玩猜拳呀
What are we doing?

742
00:41:50,241 --> 00:41:51,799
少开口，听我说
Be quiet. Listen

743
00:41:54,311 --> 00:41:56,472
我放下硬币，你用手指夹着
Try to catch the coin with your fingers

744
00:41:59,350 --> 00:42:00,840
一不教，手钝
l don't teach those slow-of-hand

745
00:42:02,586 --> 00:42:03,848
我刚才不留意嘛
l wasn't prepared just now

746
00:42:04,655 --> 00:42:05,781
再给我一次机会
Give me another chance

747
00:42:09,593 --> 00:42:11,288
二不教，眼慢
l don't teach those with slow reflexes

748
00:42:13,697 --> 00:42:14,527
你可以回去了
You can leave

749
00:42:15,599 --> 00:42:16,691
燕先生
Mr Yin

750
00:42:17,001 --> 00:42:18,127
你回去练到眼明手快
Train your reflexes

751
00:42:18,235 --> 00:42:19,099
再打电话来找我
Then call me

752
00:42:19,503 --> 00:42:20,367
多少号电话？
What's the number?

753
00:42:20,471 --> 00:42:22,029
2374213
2374213

754
00:42:22,973 --> 00:42:24,372
谢谢你再说一次
Kindly repeat that

755
00:42:24,475 --> 00:42:26,170
三不教，记性差
l don't teach those who have bad memory

756
00:42:28,312 --> 00:42:29,609
这三件事练不好
lf you can't improve in these areas

757
00:42:29,713 --> 00:42:31,476
你根本就不可能打得好麻将
You can't be a good mahjong player

758
00:42:33,651 --> 00:42:36,211
眼球灵活操第一招
Eyes training - first movement

759
00:42:38,122 --> 00:42:39,146
预备
Ready

760
00:42:39,757 --> 00:42:44,558
向上看，向下看
Look up, look down

761
00:42:44,662 --> 00:42:50,294
向左看，向右看，还原
Left, right, original position

762
00:42:51,368 --> 00:42:52,892
咕K咕K转
Rotate your eye balls

763
00:42:54,038 --> 00:42:55,665
突突眼
protrude your eye balls

764
00:42:56,540 --> 00:42:58,508
眨眨眼
Blink

765
00:42:59,777 --> 00:43:01,369
还原
Original position

766
00:43:02,313 --> 00:43:05,544
眼...
Eye

767
00:43:05,649 --> 00:43:06,843
眼什么？
What eyes?

768
00:43:06,951 --> 00:43:08,179
眼药水呀
l need eye droplets

769
00:43:08,586 --> 00:43:10,679
现在要练你手部的触觉
This is to train your hands' sensitivity

770
00:43:10,788 --> 00:43:11,311
是，师傅
Yes, teacher

771
00:43:14,258 --> 00:43:14,849
这是什么？
What's this?

772
00:43:14,959 --> 00:43:15,448
水
Water

773
00:43:15,559 --> 00:43:17,356
是人都知道是水，什么水？
Yes, but what water?

774
00:43:17,461 --> 00:43:18,359
冰水
lce water

775
00:43:18,862 --> 00:43:19,726
这个呢？
And this?

776
00:43:19,830 --> 00:43:20,489
温水
Lukewarm water

777
00:43:21,065 --> 00:43:22,259
这个呢？
And this?

778
00:43:22,366 --> 00:43:23,094
开水啊
Plain water

779
00:43:23,200 --> 00:43:23,962
不错
Not bad

780
00:43:24,535 --> 00:43:26,264
现在要提高速度反覆练习
Now repeat at high speed

781
00:43:27,137 --> 00:43:44,215
温水，开水，冰水...
Lukewarm water, plain water, ice water

782
00:43:44,722 --> 00:43:45,552
冰水
lce water

783
00:43:46,090 --> 00:43:46,715
温水
Lukewarm water

784
00:43:47,091 --> 00:43:48,251
开水
Plain water

785
00:43:48,859 --> 00:43:49,848
你自己看看
Look for yourself

786
00:43:51,562 --> 00:43:52,620
里面没有水
There's no water

787
