The grass is too long there, mow the lawn

829
00:47:02,319 --> 00:47:03,251
要每根一样
They must be of the same height

830
00:47:16,667 --> 00:47:18,897
燕先生，那些草剪好了
Mr Yin, the grass is cut

831
00:47:19,203 --> 00:47:20,568
