00:47:28,245 --> 00:47:29,678
看这几天就要起风了
lt's been quite windy these few days

833
00:47:30,080 --> 00:47:31,445
你替我拿把锯
Grab a saw

834
00:47:31,548 --> 00:47:33,038
锯掉那些没用的树枝
And cut the dead branches

835
00:47:33,150 --> 00:47:35,311
