and met many people

867
00:49:36,106 --> 00:49:38,336
看不起你，他不会教你
He wouldn't teach you
if he didn't like you

868
00:49:43,513 --> 00:49:45,674
人家明天就上山修行去了
Tomorrow is the start of hard training

869
00:49:46,116 --> 00:49:47,879
今晚千金一刻
Tonight is precious

870
00:49:48,785 --> 00:49:50,810
我也不打扰你们了，再见
l wouldn't disturb you

871
00:49:56,827 --> 00:49:57,794
等等我
Wait for me

872
00:49:59,062 --> 00:50:00,290
