l have to go home and pack my bags

873
00:50:00,797 --> 00:50:01,923
你回去吧
You may return

874
00:50:02,032 --> 00:50:03,659
我现在帮你去收拾好
l'll go and help you pack

875
00:50:03,767 --> 00:50:05,632
明天早上再回来也不迟
We can still make it tomorrow

876
00:50:06,103 --> 00:50:07,832
你进去高兴一会儿，去
Go and enjoy yourself

877
00:50:43,206 --> 00:50:44,639
这三个月你就住在这儿
You'll live here for 3 months

878
00:50:45,976 --> 00:50:47,671
让你见到的，梦到的
What you see and dream

879
00:50:47,778 --> 00:50:50,110
踢到的，睡到的，闻到的都是麻将
feel, touch, dream and smell
will be mahjong

880
00:50:50,914 --> 00:50:52,347
你跟它们多接触点
Make more contact with them

881
00:50:52,449 --> 00:50:53,438
