They all want to make Full Flush

911
00:53:25,702 --> 00:53:27,533
我呢就动也不用动
l didn't make a move

912
00:53:27,971 --> 00:53:31,338
在八圈里面胡了五铺大三元
l win 5 games
with the Three Great Scholars

