00:53:36,079 --> 00:53:37,546
六铺大四喜
6 games of the Fourfold Homely Happiness

914
00:53:56,066 --> 00:53:56,725
自摸清一色
Full Flush by drawing myself

915
00:53:56,833 --> 00:53:58,164
这招叫做一帆风顺
This is a good tactic

